                           <desc type="GuestText">
                             <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus</title>
                           </desc>
                             <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ስመ፡ መሐላ፡ ዘኢይሔሱ</q>
                              </item>

                              <item xml:id="a2">
                                <locus from="4r" to="5v"/>
                                 <desc type="GuestText">
                                   <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">በእንተ፡ ትምህርት፡ ህቡአት፡</title>
                           </desc>
                                    </item>

                                    <item xml:id="a3">
                                      <locus from="6r" to="6v"/>
                                       <desc type="GuestText">
                                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5820ArawitaGadam">አረዊተ፡ ገዳም፡</title>
                                 </desc>
                                 <note>The reference to the <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/KTXCR9DD"><seg type="bookSection"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Turaev1899Orationes"/><title level="a">Ėḟiopskija orationes falsae i exorcismi</title><title level="m">Recueil des travaux rédigés en mémoire du jubilé scientifique de Daniel Chwolson</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Boris</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Turaev</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">David</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Günzburg</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Berlin</pubPlace><publisher>S. Calvary &amp; Co.</publisher><date>1899</date><biblScope unit="page">242-267</biblScope><note type="url">http://sammlungen.ub.uni-frankfurt.de/freimann/content/pageview/806397</note><citedRange unit="page">253-254</citedRange></bibl> is not clear enough.</note>
                                          </item>

                                    <item xml:id="a4">
                                      <locus target="#139v"/>
                                      <desc type="GuestText">
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3050RepCh330">Hymn to Jesus Christ</title>
                                      </desc>
                                          <q xml:lang="gez">ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በዘባነ፡ ባሕር፡ ከመ፡ ትትለሀይ፡ ሐመር፡
                                              መንክር፡ ተላህያ፡ ለዘለከ፡ ፍቅር፨
                                         </q>

                                         <note>The hymn is composed of 15 strophes.</note>

                                          </item>

                              <item xml:id="a5">
                                <locus target="#140"/>
                                <desc type="GuestText">
